00:30:46.340 --> 00:30:48.170
The European debt
crisis is a situation

00:30:48.170 --> 00:30:50.860
in which a number of
European countries

00:30:50.860 --> 00:30:54.540
have seen their risk level
rise up in the markets,

00:30:54.540 --> 00:30:58.120
and as such, they're
unable to issue new debt.

00:30:58.120 --> 00:31:00.496
